  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Airway dendritic cells control pulmonary immune responses to inhaled particles. It is the aim
      of the present study to investigate the acute effects of smoking on the number and surface
      molecule expression of human airway dendritic cells.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
